and their lives are ruined.

00:31:04.750 --> 00:31:07.600 align:middle line:84%
You'll never recover from that--
never, ever recover from that.

00:31:07.600 --> 00:31:08.440 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: How can
you explain it?

00:31:08.440 --> 00:31:09.402 align:middle line:90%
Well, it wasn't there.

00:31:09.402 --> 00:31:10.360 align:middle line:90%
It wasn't there before.

00:31:10.360 --> 00:31:11.550 align:middle line:90%
It wasn't there yesterday.

00:31:11.550 --> 00:31:12.490 align:middle line:90%
You can't explain it.

00:31:12.490 --> 00:31:13.690 align:middle line:84%
>>PEARCE: And if
you were doing it,

00:31:13.690 --> 00:31:15.357 align:middle line:84%
you'd say exactly the
same thing anyway.

00:31:15.357 --> 00:31:17.310 align:middle line:84%
So you're never
going to be believed.

00:31:17.310 --> 00:31:19.400 align:middle line:84%
And this is so easy, and
there's different levels

00:31:19.400 --> 00:31:21.720 align:middle line:84%
set for $5, $10,
$20 or something,

00:31:21.720 --> 00:31:26.150 align:middle line:84%
you can do strange things, like
completely screw all their--

00:31:26.150 --> 00:31:28.820 align:middle line:84%
in fact, let's say that someone
would get into your Facebook

00:31:28.820 --> 00:31:32.210 align:middle line:84%
page, completely modify
your Facebook page,

00:31:32.210 --> 00:31:35.610 align:middle line:84%
and then change the password
so you can't get back in there.

00:31:35.610 --> 00:31:40.460 align:middle line:84%
So for example, they might post
terrible things about your boss

00:31:40.460 --> 00:31:42.650 align:middle line:84%
as if it was you saying
things about your boss

00:31:42.650 --> 00:31:43.940 align:middle line:90%
to get you to lose your job.

00:31:43.940 --> 00:31:47.840 align:middle line:84%
[SCOFFS] Few hundred
dollars for that, nothing.

00:31:47.840 --> 00:31:51.600 align:middle line:84%
And you can't now then go back
