So we have people who commit
these larger crimes and attempt

00:38:52.430 --> 00:38:57.620 align:middle line:84%
not that long ago on Donald
Trump's life and many others.

00:38:57.620 --> 00:39:02.600 align:middle line:84%
Now, people get confused
because people now don't trust

00:39:02.600 --> 00:39:04.470 align:middle line:90%
anybody or anything they say.

